title: MEDSAFE
cleaned_text: - [Medicines](../Medicines/medicines-landing.asp) [Devices](../devices/devices-landing.asp) [Safety](../safety/safety-landing.asp) of Vaccine Reports Reports summarising the number and type of adverse events following immunisation (AEFI) reported with COVID-19 vaccines. Please note there is a time lag between receipt of AEFI reports and publication of the report. We do not release detailed descriptions as we must protect the privacy of the people concerned.
